%F A119536 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - 6*a(n-2) + 4*a(n-3) - a(n-4); a(0)=0, a(1)=6, a(2)=30, a(3)=90. - _Harvey P. Dale_, Mar 19 2013
%F A119536 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 22 2026: (Start)
%F A119536 G.f.: 6*x*(1 + x + x^2)/(1 - x)^4.
%F A119536 E.g.f.: 3*x*(x + 1)*(x + 2)*exp(x).
%F A119536 a(n) = A008530(n)/2 for n > 0. (End)
%p A119536 [seq (3*n^3+3*n,n=0..60)];
